   {:e #blake3 "00ebf858fbaf6312dea02bcb0c56a6ea1798f7dcdf235898e150dce618a566a7" :a :task/description :v "CONTEXT: Definitive test suite proving C9 achieves 10/10. Verifies: proactive path (seed convergent findings), reactive path (steering-optimized observe with questions), invariant formalization, concept naming, fixed-point property, and steering quality.\n\nLAYER 1 — UNIT TESTS (28 tests): all_observations: (1) empty store, (2) sorted desc, (3) fields correct, (4) concept_name populated, (5) link_count correct. observe subcommands: (6) list groups by concept, (7) search ranks by composite, (8) search empty, (9) show includes links, (10) recent respects limit, (11) creation backward compat. agent identity: (12) PID default, (13) env override, (14) flag override. concept naming: (15) distinguishing keywords, (16) deterministic, (17) fallback. scoring: (18) proptest high ranks above low, (19) proptest empty corroboration = original formula. steering questions: (20) list output ends with bridge-gap question, (21) search output ends with convergent action, (22) show output ends with unlinked neighbor, (23) recent output ends with coverage gap. observation_steering_question: (24) empty store returns generic question not panic, (25) store with 2 concepts returns bridge-gap question referencing both, (26) store with 1 concept returns deepening question, (27) deterministic (same store same question), (28) question references actual concept names not hash artifacts.\n\nLAYER 2 — INVARIANT VERIFICATION (5 tests): INV-REFLEXIVE-006: (29) 10 obs from 2 agents, observe search returns top 3. (30) observe list on 50 obs shows grouped themes. (31) observe show on obs with 3 links shows targets. (32) ALL observe subcommands include steering question (grep for '->').  INV-REFLEXIVE-007: (33) find_agreement_clusters on meta-observations returns valid result.\n\nLAYER 3 — INTEGRATION (3 scenarios): (A) Proactive: 3 agents, same finding, seed has Convergent findings. (B) Reactive: 10 obs, 3 concepts, observe list groups, search ranks, show has context, ALL have steering questions. (C) Fixed-point: meta-observations produce same-format output.\n\nLAYER 4 — E2E (scripts/e2e_c9_complete.sh, 16 checks): (1) braid init. (2-4) 3 agents observe same topic. (5) 1 unrelated. (6) observe list — grouped + steering question. (7) observe search 'stagnant' — ranked + question. (8) observe search 'unrelated' — 1 result + question. (9) observe recent 2 — 2 results + question. (10) observe show — full + links + question. (11) seed synthesize — Convergent findings. (12) concept names are meaningful. (13) meta-observation works identically. (14) steering question references actual concepts. (15) steering question is different for different contexts (list vs search vs show). (16) All exit 0.\n\nLOGGING: [C9-TEST] structured, command/output/assertion/elapsed. Failure dump: datom count, observations by agent, concept inventory, agreement clusters, full outputs.\n\nDEPENDS-ON: C9-P4 (t-266f06d5), C9-P5 (t-ae7bab6f), C9-P6 (t-4807b60b), C9-SPEC (t-442a7ddd). FILES: tests/c9_second_order.rs, scripts/e2e_c9_complete.sh, inline tests. EFFORT: 6h." :op :assert}
